{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97407, "create_time": 1651660092, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "说来好笑\n我求助心理危机干预热线，发现他们的工作异常忙碌，根本排不到队；\n我求助学校的心理咨询中心，发现他们五一期间休假；\n我想去医院挂个心理咨询，发现他们的费用我根本负担不起；\n最后，我在世界的角落写下这篇遗言的时候，却突然又找到了活下去的动力。", "timestamp": 1651660092}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97411, "create_time": 1651660239, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "啊这 洞主啥情况啊？现在还好吗？", "timestamp": 1651660239}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97412, "create_time": 1651660298, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "还愿意写下这么长的文字说明还是有些念想的吧patpat", "timestamp": 1651660298}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97413, "create_time": 1651660299, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "不要想不开，要不要和我聊聊呢", "timestamp": 1651660299}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97415, "create_time": 1651660582, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: dz在哪 carol可以陪你一整晚 抱着你 不想说话的话，一句话也不必说", "timestamp": 1651660582}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97417, "create_time": 1651660691, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "谢谢Alice Bob Carol，你们让我感受到世界还存在的温暖\n我只是个和世界格格不入的人，想苟延残喘到最后一刻，看看自己的结局", "timestamp": 1651660691}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97420, "create_time": 1651660842, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "dz 你的故事我们愿意听\n", "timestamp": 1651660842}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97422, "create_time": 1651660940, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "DZ 再想想，至少给我们再讲讲你的故事，别着急离开，还有很多人关心", "timestamp": 1651660940}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97423, "create_time": 1651660988, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "dz有什么心事可以说说啊，如果想私聊，Bob愿意留个qq，千万别想不开啊", "timestamp": 1651660988}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97424, "create_time": 1651660994, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re 洞主: 不知道我能说啥，但是一定要活下去呀~", "timestamp": 1651660994}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97428, "create_time": 1651661231, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "谢谢Dave Eve的劝慰   我的故事不过是一个因为先天缺陷没有能力辨别方向的小孩儿    在不慎踏入荆棘之地后出不来了而已      具体讲起来 你们要笑掉大牙的     但是感谢你们的挽留     这是那个和我说“永别了”的人没想做的", "timestamp": 1651661231}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97431, "create_time": 1651661285, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 真的感谢你的善意     我还是怕我的故事让人笑掉大牙呢", "timestamp": 1651661285}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97432, "create_time": 1651661292, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re 洞主: dz找到了活下去的动力了呀！那是什么呀！", "timestamp": 1651661292}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97437, "create_time": 1651661432, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Grace: 为了不让19年来承受的一切白费  继续承受我应该承受的痛苦   去路的尽头看看我这种人的结局 ", "timestamp": 1651661432}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97438, "create_time": 1651661469, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 猜测dz是被骗或者被分手了？dz没有必要因为这样的事情想不开，我也不会觉得这样的事情好笑", "timestamp