, "text": "我们还年轻，还有更多的机会呢！dz还有机会见到更远的世界，认识到更多有趣的人呢！", "timestamp": 1651663287}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97523, "create_time": 1651664580, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "dz可以试一下学校24小时的心理服务热线，62785252，可能辅导的比较专业~", "timestamp": 1651664580}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97528, "create_time": 1651664733, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 14, "text": "Re 洞主: dz有什么心事可以加我qq聊聊2309547201，千万别想不开啊", "timestamp": 1651664733}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97538, "create_time": 1651665051, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 15, "text": "有些事情确实是我们没办法选择的。然而我们可以选择鲜血淋漓地抗争。唯有活下去，才有可能战胜那些伤害我们的人与事，才有机会给和我们一样的人带来些许光明。给自己一些时间处理好情绪，然后继续向生活发起冲锋。如果DZ有需要，可以和我联系，我非常愿意倾听。", "timestamp": 1651665051}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97546, "create_time": 1651665218, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 15, "text": "Re 洞主: qq1517725639", "timestamp": 1651665218}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97560, "create_time": 1651666265, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "感谢各位，我会向前看的", "timestamp": 1651666265}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97593, "create_time": 1651667567, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 16, "text": "￣□￣｜｜ 差不多得了", "timestamp": 1651667567}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97599, "create_time": 1651667676, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Paul: 你别用这样的语气说话好吗", "timestamp": 1651667676}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 97602, "create_time": 1651667756, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, 